SUMMARY:SNAP Summer Tour 2026
DESCRIPTION:This summer\, Houston Food Bank’s Community Assistance Program (CAP) is hitting the road! Our SNAP Mobile Unit will be traveling throughout the Greater Houston area to help individuals and families apply for SNAP and other vital programs. Stop by to connect with our team of trained navigators and learn how we can support you with application assistance for: \n\nSNAP (Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program)\nTANF (Temporary Assistance for Needy Families)\nCHIP & CHIP Perinatal\nMedicaid\nMedicare Savings Program\nHealthy Texas Women\n\nNo appointment needed—just come by and get the help you need\, close to home. \nTour Dates and LocationsNew Hope Housing- Harrisburg \n\nFriday\, June 5th 9 am- 3 pm\n3315 Harrisburg Blvd\, Houston\, TX 77003\n\n  \nBrazoria County Pride Fest \n\nSaturday\, June 6th from 10 am- 3 pm\nMacLean Park- 93 Lake Road\, Lake Jackson\, TX 77566\n\n  \nFamily Free Day at Children’s Museum Houston \n\nThursday\, June 11th 5- 8 pm\n1500 Binz St\, Houston\, TX 77004\n\n  \nUrban Market in 3rd Ward \n\nSaturday\, June 13th from 10 am – 1pm\n2600 Holman St.\, Houston\, TX 77004\n\n  \nLord of the Streets (LOTS) \n\nFriday\, June 26th from 7 am- 1 pm\n3401 Fannin St\, Houston\, TX 77004\n\n  \nAccess Care of Coastal Texas (ACCT) \n\nSaturday\, June 27th from 11 am- 3 pm\n707 23rd St\, Galveston\, TX 77550\n\n  \nHearts and Hands of Baytown Food Pantry \n\nTuesday\, July 7th from 9 am- 2 pm\n307 Cedar Bayou Rd\, Baytown\, TX 77520\n\n  \nNew Hope Housing-Reed \n\nFriday\, July 10th from 9 am- 3 pm\n2605 Reed Rd\, Houston\, TX 77051\n\n  \nCatholic Charities Guadalupe Area Social Services \n\nThursday\, July 16th from 8 am- 1 pm\n326 S Jensen Dr\, Houston\, TX 77003\n\n  \nBack to School Fair at St Austin Center \n\nSaturday\, July 25th from 9 am- 12 pm\n2002 S Wayside Dr\, Houston\, Texas 77023\n\n  \nMayor’s Back 2 School & Health Fair  \n\nSaturday\, August 1st from 8 am- 2 pm\nGeorge R. Brown Convention Center\, 1001 Avenida de las Americas\, Houston\, TX 77010\n\n  \nBakerRipley Pasadena Campus \n\nTuesday\, August 4th from 8 am- 2 pm\n720 Fairmont Pkwy\, Pasadena\, TX 77504\n\n  \nBayland Community Center \n\nFriday\, August 7th from 8 am- 3 pm\n6400 Bissonnet St\, Houston\, TX 77074\n\nEl Franco Lee Community Center \n\nFriday\, August 14th from 8 am-3 pm\n9500 Hall Rd\, Houston\, TX 77089
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/snap-summer-tour-2026/
CATEGORIES:Community Assistance,FEATURED,SNAP
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/SNAP-Summer-Tour-2026-1200x900-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
