SUMMARY:The Reggie and Ron Radiothon
DESCRIPTION:Sports Radio 610 is hosting their 2nd annual The Reggie and Ron Radiothon benefiting Houston Food Bank on July 3\, 2026. Reggie and Ron host this show from 6 a.m. – 6 p.m.. There will be a special appearance from an HFB President Brian Greene to talk more on food insecurity and how donations can impact our neighbors. \nTune in to 610 AM to listen live and support this fundraiser by texting 2026Radiothon to 71777 or by visiting their donation page: Sports Radio 610 Radiothon.
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/the-reggie-and-ron-radiothon/
CATEGORIES:FEATURED,Fund Drive,Special Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Radioathon-1200x900-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
