SUMMARY:Community Conversation Volunteer Shift
DESCRIPTION:Join a truly unique volunteer shift where neighbors\, community leaders\, and food bank staff come together to share experiences and bridge mutual understanding. The gathering is highly interactive and uses structured conversations to build stronger and more connected communities. Whether you join individually or as a group\, this experience moves beyond food distribution to focus on lasting community impact! \nRegister Here
