SUMMARY:ABC13 Loves Teachers
DESCRIPTION:ABC13 and their community partners are coming together to stuff school buses with school supplies to benefit Houston Food Bank’s School Programs! On the date of the supply drive day\, Channel 13 will broadcast live from the station to tell the story of the program\, how it impacts amazing teachers and students\, and to encourage people to donate. Channel 13 will do interviews with teachers\, schools and students to tell their story of how the program helps them and why it is important. These interviews will run in advance of the drive date and also during the event date.
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/abc13-loves-teachers/
CATEGORIES:ABC Loves Teachers,Special Event,Teachers Aid Drive
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ABC-loves-teachers-1200x900-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
