SUMMARY:Mayor's Back 2 School and Health Fair
DESCRIPTION:When:August 1\, 2026 \nWhat:The Annual Mayor’s Back 2 School and Health Fair presented by Shell provides 20\,000 Houston area students with the tools they need to start the school year off right. In addition to distributing 20\,000 backpacks with school supplies\, the event will feature on-site health screenings to include: dental screenings and sealants\, vision screenings\, mental health screenings\, and routine immunizations. The event also connects families to a wide range of health and social services offered by community agencies. \nWhere:George R. Brown Convention Center
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/mayors-back-2-school-and-health-fair/
LOCATION:George R Brown Convention Center\, 1001 Avenida de las Americas\, Houston\, TX\, 77010\, United States
CATEGORIES:Back to School Fest,FEATURED,Special Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/MayorsBack2School-1200x900-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
